replies.body:
I like the new cursor design, but perhaps the whole cursor should change colour when hovering an enemy or ally, or at least the back end. Also for warding, you could add a small ward icon next to the cursor that changes colour with ward type and maybe a brush icon when hovering over a brush. I just think it'll look better.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 
Disclaimer: not all of these are my ideas.
